This year, we asked y’all to nominate someone you know who isn’t home on Christmas due to being active duty, first responder, law enforcement, healthcare, etc.
•
After receiving thousands of emails and nominations (wow!), we picked a few nominees and sent them some Yee Yee gear to brighten their Christmas while away from loved ones.
•
Here are a few of those people and their incredible stories. #Heroes
•
🎥: @briankimble
